{{作品名稱|name=''Spartacus''|hk=風雲群英會|tw=萬夫莫敵|cn=斯巴达克斯}}是一套1960年的[[美國電影|美國]][[傳記|傳記]]片，由[[史丹利·寇比力克|史丹利·寇比力克]]執導，[[卻·德格拉斯|卻·德格拉斯]]等主演。電影以[[斯巴达克斯|斯巴達克斯]]的經歷為藍本，描述他率領奴隸[[斯巴达克斯起义|起義]]對抗[[古羅馬|羅馬]]人的故事。获得[[金球奖最佳戏剧类影片|金球奖最佳戏剧类影片]]。

== 演員表 ==
* [[寇克·道格拉斯|寇克·道格拉斯]] 飾 Spartacus [[斯巴达克斯|斯巴達克斯]]
:[[色雷斯人|色雷斯人]]奴隸，原在[[利比亞|利比亞]]工作，後成為名[[角鬥士|角鬥士]]，更率領奴隸起義
* [[勞倫斯·奧立佛|勞倫斯·奧立佛]] 飾 Crassus [[馬庫斯·李錫尼·克拉蘇|克拉蘇]]
:古羅馬[[貴族_(古羅馬)|貴族]]，對羅馬及其政治制度極為忠心
* [[珍·西蒙絲|珍·西蒙絲]] 飾 Varinia
:在角鬥士學校工作的女奴，來自[[不列顛尼亞|不列顛尼亞]]，後愛上[[斯巴达克斯|斯巴達克斯]]，嫁給他後更為他誕下兒子
* [[查爾斯·勞頓|查爾斯·勞頓]] 飾 Gracchus
<!---:a dedicated Roman senator who is Crassus's only real opposition. He is a Republican and a crooked pragmatist whose lack of scruples in his political dealings is his ultimate downfall.--->
* [[皮特·烏斯蒂諾夫|皮特·烏斯蒂諾夫]] 飾 Lentulus Batiatus
<!---:a shrewd, manipulative slave dealer, who purchases Spartacus, and ends up paying dearly for it. He blames Crassus for Spartacus's rebellion and for his poverty; therefore, he seeks revenge against Crassus and eventually settles that account with a little help from the Roman senator Gracchus. Peter Ustinov won his first Oscar for his role in this film; his performance was the only one to win an Oscar in a film directed by Kubrick.--->
* [[John_Gavin|John Gavin]] 飾 [[恺撒|恺撒]]
<!---:the young ambitious protege of Gracchus, who gains command of the Garrison of Rome during the chaos of the Spartacus rebellion.--->
* [[Nina_Foch|Nina Foch]] 飾 Helena Glabrus
<!---:a shrewd, manipulative sister of Marcus Publius Glabrus, who insists that Batiatus entertain them with two pairs of gladiators fighting to the death.--->
* [[John_Ireland_(actor)|John Ireland]] 飾 [[Crixus|Crixus]]
<!---:one of Spartacus' most loyal lieutenants, and serves him until he is slain in the final battle. Academy Award–nominee Ireland normally played supporting roles.--->
* [[Herbert_Lom|Herbert Lom]] 飾 Tigranes Levantus
<!---:a [[奇里乞亞|奇里乞亞]]n pirate who agrees to take the slaves out of Italy. When Spartacus and his forces reach [[布林迪西|布林迪西]], Levantus is forced to betray them, and takes no pride in it.--->
* [[John_Dall|John Dall]] 飾 Marcus Publius Glabrus
<!---:a naïve protege of Crassus, who unwittingly plays into the hands of Gracchus. Academy Award–nominee Dall was an American actor who worked primarily in the theatre.--->
* [[Charles_McGraw|Charles McGraw]] 飾 Marcellus
<!---:the gruff gladiator trainer for Lentulus Batiatus. He dislikes Spartacus immediately and singles him out for extra training and punishment. He is killed by Spartacus during the revolt.--->
* [[東尼·柯蒂斯|東尼·柯蒂斯]] 飾 Antoninus
<!---:a young [[西西里島|西西里島]]n slave who leaves his master, Crassus, and joins Spartacus. At the conclusion of the movie, [[Spartacus|Spartacus]] and Antoninus are forced to fight to the death in a gladiatorial match, the survivor to be [[crucified|crucified]].--->
* [[Woody_Strode|Woody Strode]] 飾 Draba
<!---:an [[埃塞俄比亞|埃塞俄比亞]]n being trained at the gladiatorial school. Initially, Draba refuses to tell Spartacus his name, as he knows someday he might be matched with him in the ring: each would be obliged to kill the other.--->

